{"tid":1646722,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"選前政見全跳票！市民嗆「後悔投給你」將市長綁車尾拖行","createTime":"2019-10-11T12:11:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T12:46:40.000Z","uid":235152,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9f4332c6995681b3f834b66fb79fc204595d9352","tid":1646722,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T12:11:44.000Z","msg":"國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n選舉時候選人都會提出許多政見、競選承諾，但是在當選後有沒有辦法兌現都備受考驗，某些只會說大話、喊口號的政治人物，一定都會在下一次選舉被選民用選票教訓，不過國外的選民可沒有這麼溫和，一名墨西哥市長就因為承諾沒兌現，被市民綁車尾沿街拖行洩憤。<br />\n<br />\n根據外媒報導，這起事件發生在墨西哥，這位市長名叫Jorge Luis Escandon Hernandez，他在競選期間曾開出支票，承諾市民一定會「把道路鋪平零坑洞」，答應會停止許多無謂的施工，以降低道路發生車禍的機率，還再三保證絕對說到做到。<br />\n<br />\n然而當選後「支票放水流」，這名說大話的市長不但沒有兌現承諾，還再三的找藉口推託，這讓許多當初投票給他的市民不滿，覺得自己遭受到欺騙，在野黨們也對市長的政見跳票相當生氣，就這樣民怨不斷累積之下，市民終於爆發了。<br />\n<br />\n在10月8日這天，一群民眾來到當地的政府機關，衝到市長所在的辦公室內，先是用繩子綁住市長的雙手，接著再強行將人拉出辦公大樓，並與政府機關的工作人員發生衝突，接著把市長綁在車子後方沿街拖行，市民更怒嗆「這樣做的目的是要讓市長，親身感受遺下道路的危險」。<br />\n<br />\n接著網路上開始瘋傳這段「市長遭拖行影片」，從影片中可以看出來，這輛貨車的車速非常快，市長就穿著襯衫牛仔褲被市民拖行，警方獲報後出動了大批警力，才終於成功將市長救出，整起事件共造成20人受傷，市長送醫急救後沒有生命危險，而有數十人被警察逮捕。（黃韻璇報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/sdpnoticias/status/1181744037876903937?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1181744037876903937&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D616351\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fsdpnoticias%2Fstatus%2F1181744037876903937%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1181744037876903937%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.setn.com%252Fm%252Fnews.aspx%253Fnewsid%253D616351&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwcqjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=4b7781e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/sdpnoticias/status/1181744037876903937?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1181744037876903937&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D616351</a>"},{"pid":"d166b1d2d651903a340d2e4c6dfb13c0ee2bc13e","tid":1646722,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T12:12:41.000Z","msg":"突發！香城online現已公開發售！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1646714\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1646714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1a11c04bba5ef5045814c0f7348eeef203d1b27f","tid":1646722,"uid":301092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T12:18:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SKwtamG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSKwtamG.jpg&h=fae8ffd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大驚小怪 玩滑水咁姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(聽聞何君堯議員好熱愛水上運動<br />\n香港人幾時邀請佢一齊滑下水)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098d46c95dfa8b430902e27bb408b2f30d3f4ee2","tid":1646722,"uid":59447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T12:18:30.000Z","msg":"香港市市長呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35844c1e0892770e1f9ebb0ed7d64fb0167f9157","tid":1646722,"uid":193233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T12:26:00.000Z","msg":"香港人唔好再示弱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c05fb8a6223764cd50867729b9146f3feb672f","tid":1646722,"uid":331421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T12:32:32.000Z","msg":"香港幾時有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff7e010ac61b702f7a4f642d6289aa12486020e2","tid":1646722,"uid":238370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T12:46:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}